      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  x-ope                      pic  x(02)                  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * File name                                             *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  x-nam                      pic  x(04)                  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * File pathname                                         *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  x-pat                      pic  x(40)                  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * File status                                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  x-sts                      pic  x(02)                  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * File record                                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  x-rec.
               10  x-chr        occurs 80 pic  x(01)                  .

