      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Main program                                              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       main-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open output foreground                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        m-ope                =    "OF"
                     perform out-frg-000  thru out-frg-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open output background                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           else if   m-ope                =    "OB"
                     perform out-bkg-000  thru out-bkg-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Write                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           else if   m-ope                =    "WR"
                     perform wrt-wrt-000  thru wrt-wrt-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open input foreground                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           else if   m-ope                =    "IF"
                     perform inp-frg-000  thru inp-frg-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open input background                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           else if   m-ope                =    "IB"
                     perform inp-bkg-000  thru inp-bkg-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Read                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           else if   m-ope                =    "RD"
                     perform rea-rea-000  thru rea-rea-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close input                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           else if   m-ope                =    "CI"
                     perform cls-inp-000  thru cls-inp-999            .
       main-999.
           exit      program.

